p: Mechanical testing of the electrospun membranes was indicated in Figure 6 and Table 4. The tensile testing clearly indicated that the tensile strength of the pristine PU was enhanced on incorporating PM and CuSO 4. PU showed a tensile strength of 6.83 MPa and, on adding PM and CuSO 4, it was increased to 7.04 MPa and 13.60 MPa, respectively.
